strings: <voice_0x01000E64><se_low>King Trode: Hm? Is that a castle?
<voice_0x01000E65><se_low>King Trode: Let's see... If my memory serves me correctly...

<voice_0x01000E66><se_low>King Trode: This must be... Yes!
It's the Kingdom of Argonia!

<voice_0x01000E67><se_low>King Trode: My daughter is due to marry the Prince of
this realm.
<voice_0x01000E68><se_low>King Trode: Well, well, well...Argonia indeed. That means you'll undoubtedly meet King Clavius and Prince Charmles when you go to collect the magic mirror.
<voice_0x01000E69><se_low>King Trode: And when that happens, you must keep the current condition of the Princess and I absolutely secret!
<voice_0x01000E6A><se_low>King Trode: If anyone enquires as to the purpose of your travels, tell them you are hunting the villain known as Dhoulmagus and nothing more.
<voice_0x01000E6B><se_low>King Trode: In any case, there's no way the Princess and I can enter the kingdom looking as we do.

<voice_0x01000E6C><se_low>King Trode: We have Dhoulmagus's treachery to thank
for that.
<voice_0x01000E6D><se_low>King Trode: All the more reason to find him and put an end to his schemes as quickly as possible.
<voice_0x01000E6E><se_low>King Trode: I'm not about to let Dhoulmagus's hellish curse cheat my daughter of a match made in heaven!
